{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_05_03",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 05 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おいっしょ……う～ん、日本酒って\n結構重たいなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heave-ho… Hmm‚ sake is\npretty heavy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.877528286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 8.077528286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、優ちゃん、危ないよ！\n一本ずつでいいから、あんまり無理しないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Yu-chan‚ be careful!\nJust carry one bottle at a time‚ don't overexert yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.077528286,
      "endTime": 14.1121541023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.3188205401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、ラベルを貼るのって意外と難しいのね\nなかなか真っすぐにならないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ putting on labels is surprisingly difficult.\nI can't seem to get them straight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3188205401,
      "endTime": 21.6503399532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.857006391
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、それは私がやるから\n二人とも、そろそろ休憩して！　もうお昼過ぎてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ I'll do that‚\nso you two take a break! It's already past lunchtime!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.857006391,
      "endTime": 29.4705892882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 29.6772559167
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてんの、うちらまだまだ働くって～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? We're still going to work~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6772559167,
      "endTime": 33.63022693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、レッスンで鍛えてるから\n体力には自信があるもの。もっと手伝わせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ we've been training in lessons‚\nso we're confident in our stamina. Let us help you more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8968935967,
      "endTime": 40.5513963558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 40.7411340078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "き、気持ちは嬉しいんだけど……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-Thanks for the thought‚ but… Ahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7411340078,
      "endTime": 45.139501222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 46.2078006745
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 46.2078006745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃんは\n私に「夢を追え」って言ってくれたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My brother\ntold me to \"chase my dreams\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2411340078,
      "endTime": 52.6690948985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 52.8744673412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "私にとって最初の夢は……\nお兄ちゃんがプロのピアニストになることだったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But my first dream…\nwas for my brother to become a professional pianist.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8744673412,
      "endTime": 59.0238096419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 59.2411340078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんや……もしかして\nアイドルを目指したのも、そのためやったん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so… Could it be\nthat you aimed to become an idol for that reason?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2411340078,
      "endTime": 65.50696150179999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、ごめんね。子役の仕事がなくなって\nお兄ちゃんの留学資金を稼げなくなったからなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ I'm sorry. My child acting jobs dried up‚\nand I couldn't earn money for my brother's study abroad anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7411340078,
      "endTime": 75.7962422985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 76.0078006745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん今は、「三人でトップアイドルになる」って\n私自身の、もう一つの夢を見つけた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ now I've found another dream of my own:\n\"to become a top idol with the three of us\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0078006745,
      "endTime": 83.2575331626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "けど……お兄ちゃんのピアノは、悲しそうだった\nお兄ちゃんは、本当はピアノを諦めたくないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… my brother's piano sounded sad.\nMy brother doesn't really want to give up on piano.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1,
      "endTime": 96.1283220927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 96.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "なのに……私一人だけが夢を追い続けて\n本当にいいのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… is it really okay for me\nto keep pursuing my dream alone…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3666666667,
      "endTime": 104.4560320854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 104.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6333333333,
      "endTime": 106.2921993254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 106.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "えらいなぁ、すみれちゃんは、まだ中学生やのに\nそんなに沢山背負って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's amazing‚ Sumire-chan. You're still a middle school student‚\nyet you're carrying so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5666666667,
      "endTime": 113.2231080292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 113.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、そんな風に思い詰めたらあかんよ\nうちらに頼って？　なぁ、瑠依ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you shouldn't bottle it all up like that.\nRely on us. Right‚ Rui-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333333333,
      "endTime": 120.88821281999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 121.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "優の言う通りよ、すみれ\n……そうだ！　いいことを思いついたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu is right‚ Sumire.\n…That's it! I have a good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1,
      "endTime": 127.73995872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 127.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私と優もお店を手伝う\nその分、すみれのお父様には休んでもらいましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu and I will help out at the shop.\nThat way‚ your father can rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9666666667,
      "endTime": 133.64852034129999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 133.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　で、でも、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんに\n酒蔵の仕事なんて、させられないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? B-But we can't let Rui-chan and Yu-chan\ndo brewery work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8333333333,
      "endTime": 141.3284783044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 141.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫や、うちらが根性あるんは\nすみれちゃんも知ってるやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry. You know\nhow tough we are‚ Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.5333333333,
      "endTime": 146.59782006240002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 146.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、任せて、すみれ。私達がこの奥山酒造を\n酒造メーカーの頂点に立たせてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ leave it to us‚ Sumire. We'll make this Okuyama Brewery\nthe top sake brewery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8,
      "endTime": 154.2143724762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 154.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
