      "text": "で、でも……それじゃあ、お兄ちゃんは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But… then‚ what about you‚ big brother?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.1,
      "endTime": 313.7005895615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
