      "text": "……でも、お兄ちゃんだって\nピアニストになる夢が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ you too‚ big brother‚\nhad a dream of becoming a pianist…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 338.3333333333,
